replies.body:
{{champion:81}} 

As a support player I'm tired of having to support him. The laning phase is rough enough with all the problematic supports. {{champion:555}} {{champion:555}} {{champion:555}} {{champion:53}} {{champion:267}} {{champion:12}} {{champion:63}} {{champion:555}} {{champion:555}} {{champion:555}} 

Junglers aren't really providing counter pressure for bot lane lately, so if you can't keep a presence in lane, then you're gonna get trampled on. 

If you're playing a problematic support and you're managing to keep your heads above water, then the inevitable 4 man will come bot to crush your lane so the ADC can move on to crushing other lanes.

I'm so tired of supporting {{champion:81}} .

{{champion:238}} 

I'm sure everyone and their mother knows why.

Such a frustrating piece of shit.

{{champion:122}} 
Way too dominant against melees in the top lane. 
Once he snowballs he takes over the whole game.

{{champion:29}} 

Even though he hasn't been in my games as of recently, stealth is *BROKEN*. Especially twitch, because of the way his kit works with stealth.

